fsetBlur\". The two first primitives just created a drop shadow.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"step_3","title":"Step 3","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>feSpecularLighting</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">in</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>offsetBlur<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">surfaceScale</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>5<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">specularConstant</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>.75<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">specularExponent</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>20<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">lighting-color</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>#bbbbbb<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">result</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>specOut<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>fePointLight</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">x</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>-5000<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">y</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>-10000<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">z</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>20000<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>feSpecularLighting</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p><a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feSpecularLighting\"><code>&lt;feSpecularLighting&gt;</code></a> takes <code>in</code> \"offsetBlur\", generates a lighting effect, and stores the <code>result</code> in the buffer \"specOut\".</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"step_4","title":"Step 4","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>feComposite</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">in</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>specOut<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">in2</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>SourceAlpha<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">operator</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>in<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">result</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>specOut<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The first <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feComposite\"><code>&lt;feComposite&gt;</code></a> takes <code>in</code> \"specOut\" and \"SourceAlpha\", masks out the result of \"specOut\" so that the result is not bigger than \"SourceAlpha\" (the original source graphic), and overrides the <code>result</code> \"specOut\".</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"step_5","title":"Step 5","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>feComposite</span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">in</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>SourceGraphic<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">in2</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>specOut<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">operator</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>arithmetic<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">k1</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">k2</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">k3</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>1<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">k4</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>0<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token attr-name\">result</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>litPaint<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>The second <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feComposite\"><code>&lt;feComposite&gt;</code></a> takes <code>in</code> \"SourceGraphic\" and \"specOut\", adds the result of \"specOut\" on top of \"SourceGraphic\", and stores the <code>result</code> in \"litPaint\".</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"step_6","title":"Step 6","isH3":true,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: html notranslate\"><code><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>feMerge</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>feMergeNode</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">in</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>offsetBlur<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n  <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>feMergeNode</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">in</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>litPaint<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">/&gt;</span></span>\n<span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;/</span>feMerge</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">&gt;</span></span>\n</code></pre></div>\n<p>Finally, <a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feMerge\"><code>&lt;feMerge&gt;</code></a> merges together \"offsetBlur\", which is the drop shadow, and \"litPaint\", which is the original source graphic with a lighting effect.</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects/filters01-0.png\" alt=\"Source graphic\" width=\"115\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>Source graphic</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects/filters01-1.png\" alt=\"Primitive 1\" width=\"115\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>Primitive 1</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects/filters01-2.png\" alt=\"Primitive 2\" width=\"115\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>Primitive 2</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects/filters01-3.png\" alt=\"Primitive 3\" width=\"115\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>Primitive 3</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects/filters01-4.png\" alt=\"Primitive 4\" width=\"115\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>Primitive 4</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects/filters01-5.png\" alt=\"Primitive 5\" width=\"115\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>Primitive 5</p>\n<p>\n  <img src=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects/filters01-6.png\" alt=\"Primitive 6\" width=\"115\" height=\"70\" loading=\"lazy\">\n</p>\n<p>Primitive 6</p><ul class=\"prev-next\">\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Other_content_in_SVG\">« Previous</a></li>\n    <li><a class=\"button minimal\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/SVG_fonts\">Next  »</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"Example","id":"example"}],"summary":"There are situations, where basic shapes do not provide the flexibility you need to achieve a certain effect. Drop shadows, to provide a popular example, cannot be created reasonably with a combination of gradients. Filters are SVG's mechanism to create sophisticated effects.","popularity":0.0006,"modified":"2022-09-14T09:40:22.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Filtres","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"フィルター効果","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"Фильтры","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"滤镜效果","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"en-us/web/svg/tutorial/filter_effects","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/blob/style/old/files/en-us/web/svg/tutorial/filter_effects/index.md","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/content/commit/dc86333db6b97ee7fed053f76f6d0a6ecec763e9","filename":"index.md"},"parents":[{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web","title":"Web technology for developers"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG","title":"SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial","title":"SVG Tutorial"},{"uri":"/en-US/docs/Web/SVG/Tutorial/Filter_effects","title":"Filter effects"}],"pageTitle":"Filter effects - SVG: Scalable Vector Graphics | MDN","noIndexing":false}}